cold but with a strong wind. We go into the garden but there's no
work to do. Today I was bored to tears!
</P>
<P>
   Jan. 3:
</P>
<P>
   Alexei also started German measles, but quite mildly. Olga and
Tatiana are feeling better; the latter even got up. It snowed all
