</P>
<P>
   Feb. 27:
</P>
<P>
   We are going to have to considerably reduce our expenditures on
household supplies and staff, as the department of appanages
(supporting the royal family) is being closed down from March 1,
added to which we are only allowed to receive 600 rubles a month
each from our personal capital. For the last few days we have been
