</P>
<P>
   This morning we saw from the window that the little mountain has
been destroyed; it appears that the idiotic detachment committee
decided to do this in order to stop us climbing up onto it and
looking over the fence!
</P>
<P>
   nn
</P>
<P>
   (BEGIN ITALICS HERE)On March 13, the deposed monarch
acknowledges small kindnesses:(END ITALICS HERE)
</P>
<P>
   A similar day with 12 degrees of frost. I finished ``Anna
Karenina'' and began reading Lermontov. Sawed a lot of wood with
Tatiana.
</P>
<P>
   Over the last few days we have begun to receive butter, coffee,
