<P>
   (BEGIN ITALICS HERE)July 16, Alexandra's last diary entry:(END
ITALICS HERE)
</P>
<P>
   (Niece) Irena's 23d birthday. Gray morning, later lovely
sunshine. Baby has a slight cold. All went out {-hour in the
morning. Olga and I arrange our medicines. Tatiana read spiritual
readings.
</P>
<P>
   They went out. Tatiana stayed with me and we read: The Book of
the prophet Amos and prophet Audios.
</P>
<P>
   Every morning the commandant comes to our rooms: at last after a
week brought eggs again for Baby. 8 supper. Suddenly Lenka Sednev
(the kitchen boy) was fetched to go and see his uncle and flew off
