shut. ``Freezing!'' said the man, who wore a fur-trimmed parka
inside the restaurant. ``Are you kidding?'' Fran said, fanning
herself. ``It's sweltering out there.'' By E.J. MONTINI. Story will
move in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories.
